original_title: Chikara: From Zero to Hero (& Castagnoli)
overview: A 1-night tournament sees 8 tag teams fight for three points (and a title shot against Chris Hero and Claudio Castagnoli)! Mike Quackenbush, Shane Storm & Eddie Kingston partner together for revenge against Chris Hero, Claudio Castagnoli & Larry Sweeney!
title: Chikara: From Zero to Hero (& Castagnoli)
